1
00:00:01,084 --> 00:00:03,211
Because I liked it,

2
00:00:03,211 --> 00:00:04,838
just because I liked being with you,

3
00:00:04,838 --> 00:00:06,881
I endured those boring times.

4
00:00:07,173 --> 00:00:08,633
Siwoo, it's not like that.

5
00:00:08,633 --> 00:00:11,886
But I guess you hate it more when others misunderstand us.

6
00:00:12,595 --> 00:00:16,474
So much that my kindness feels burdensome and uncomfortable.

7
00:00:16,766 --> 00:00:18,393
I was just thinking of you...

8
00:00:18,393 --> 00:00:20,311
More like you were thinking of yourself.

9
00:00:20,311 --> 00:00:22,522
You just hate being misunderstood.

10
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:27,861
Just me being here with you, in itself,

11
00:00:27,861 --> 00:00:31,156
is something that causes misunderstandings.

12
00:00:33,366 --> 00:00:35,201
Hey, Kim Siwoo.

13
00:00:36,202 --> 00:00:38,872
Just as you want,

14
00:00:38,872 --> 00:00:40,790
from now on, I'll stay out of your business.

15
00:00:41,291 --> 00:00:42,208
Happy now?

16
00:00:44,544 --> 00:00:48,423
There was no need to worry about it in the first place.

17
00:00:48,423 --> 00:00:50,258
Why did I even hide it?

18
00:00:51,009 --> 00:00:51,509
What?

19
00:00:53,178 --> 00:00:55,013
Forget it.

20
00:00:56,097 --> 00:01:00,268
From the start, I could never remain just your friend for the rest of my life anyway.

21
00:01:03,021 --> 00:01:04,689
Hey, Kim Siwoo!

22
00:01:07,108 --> 00:01:11,404
What's so good about a coward like me?

23
00:01:11,404 --> 00:01:15,909
Why do you like someone who doesn't even have the courage to accept your confession?

24
00:01:15,909 --> 00:01:17,535
Making me feel so sorry.

25
00:01:28,463 --> 00:01:30,173
Lee Seongjae told me to bring this to you.

26
00:01:30,173 --> 00:01:31,883
Yeah. Thanks.

27
00:01:31,966 --> 00:01:34,219
Do you feel a bit relieved now?

28
00:01:34,469 --> 00:01:37,472
No. Not at all.

29
00:01:37,806 --> 00:01:39,557
Now Lee Seongjae knows too.

30
00:01:39,557 --> 00:01:41,643
He must have seen your wallpaper, right?

31
00:01:41,768 --> 00:01:45,230
Since he probably saw the other things too...

32
00:01:45,230 --> 00:01:47,649
he probably won't ever see me again.

33
00:01:47,649 --> 00:01:50,777
Other things?

34
00:01:50,777 --> 00:01:53,655
How much I like Lee Seongjae...

35
00:01:53,655 --> 00:01:55,824
It's all in here.

36
00:01:58,743 --> 00:02:01,329
Isn't it better to just confess and get rejected?

37
00:02:01,454 --> 00:02:04,457
I feel like that would make it easier to move on.

38
00:02:04,457 --> 00:02:05,583
I don't want to.

39
00:02:05,583 --> 00:02:06,751
It's sad to get rejected.

40
00:02:07,043 --> 00:02:09,420
And him finding out your feelings and distancing himself isn't sad?

41
00:02:09,546 --> 00:02:11,256
It's better than getting rejected.

42
00:02:11,381 --> 00:02:13,091
Liar.

43
00:02:13,091 --> 00:02:15,385
If you're going to lie, at least make it believable.

44
00:02:18,638 --> 00:02:22,934
A few days ago.

45
00:02:26,271 --> 00:02:28,022
Did you finish the research?

46
00:02:28,022 --> 00:02:32,193
We need to organize it and make the PPT today.

47
00:02:33,111 --> 00:02:34,529
I finished it, but...

48
00:02:34,529 --> 00:02:36,990
I don't have it with me.

49
00:02:38,449 --> 00:02:40,326
What nonsense are you talking about?

50
00:02:40,326 --> 00:02:41,828
Lee Seongjae has it.

51
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,204
What?

52
00:02:43,204 --> 00:02:44,747
Why does Lee Seongjae have it?

53
00:02:44,956 --> 00:02:46,332
We're not even in the same group.

54
00:02:46,332 --> 00:02:48,334
The materials...

55
00:02:48,334 --> 00:02:49,419
are on my laptop,

56
00:02:49,419 --> 00:02:52,839
and Lee Seongjae has it right now.

57
00:02:54,007 --> 00:02:55,550
Get it from Lee Seongjae.

58
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:56,885
He probably knows the password.

59
00:02:57,177 --> 00:02:58,887
Did you guys fight?

60
00:03:02,223 --> 00:03:03,474
If you had fought,

61
00:03:03,474 --> 00:03:05,602
Kim Siwoo wouldn't have this kind of expression.

62
00:03:05,602 --> 00:03:07,729
It has to be something worth fighting over to fight.

63
00:03:07,979 --> 00:03:10,481
I'm just unilaterally angry at him.

64
00:03:10,565 --> 00:03:11,649
If it's something Lee Seongjae does,

65
00:03:11,649 --> 00:03:13,902
Kim Siwoo, who accepts everything, is angry?

66
00:03:13,943 --> 00:03:15,153
At Lee Seongjae?

67
00:03:15,361 --> 00:03:17,238
I'm angry at myself.

68
00:03:18,281 --> 00:03:21,701
There was no need to try so hard to hide it...

69
00:03:21,701 --> 00:03:25,413
I'm just taking my annoyance out on Lee Seongjae,

70
00:03:25,413 --> 00:03:26,873
who gave me an excuse.

71
00:03:28,583 --> 00:03:30,877
Did Lee Seongjae do something weird to you?

72
00:03:31,294 --> 00:03:33,421
Something weird?

73
00:03:37,425 --> 00:03:39,677
That guy, Lee Seongjae...

74
00:03:39,969 --> 00:03:42,180
is just an idiot.

75
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:46,100
He still doesn't know how much I like him.

76
00:03:54,234 --> 00:03:56,319
Are you really planning to drink yourself to death?

77
00:03:56,486 --> 00:03:58,404
Stop drinking.

78
00:04:01,574 --> 00:04:02,825
Who's dying?

79
00:04:05,662 --> 00:04:08,081
I do feel like dying, though.

80
00:04:09,874 --> 00:04:10,875
Dojin.

81
00:04:12,293 --> 00:04:15,088
Kim Siwoo isn't picking up his phone.

82
00:04:15,213 --> 00:04:17,548
See? Why did you talk nonsense?

83
00:04:17,924 --> 00:04:21,594
You're the one who told Kim Siwoo to stay away.

84
00:04:22,220 --> 00:04:25,098
I thought we could remain friends if I did that.

85
00:04:26,724 --> 00:04:30,853
I really didn't mean to hurt Siwoo.

86
00:04:30,853 --> 00:04:33,773
How could I possibly hurt Siwoo?

87
00:04:33,773 --> 00:04:36,609
Who am I to do that?

88
00:04:42,031 --> 00:04:43,616
At least your self-awareness is on point.

89
00:05:07,598 --> 00:05:09,309
I'm dying here, Siwoo.

90
00:05:09,309 --> 00:05:10,643
Just this once.

91
00:05:10,643 --> 00:05:12,186
Please do something about this bastard Lee Seongjae.

92
00:05:12,186 --> 00:05:14,981
He's just chugging alcohol.

93
00:05:36,753 --> 00:05:37,879
Hey, please save me.

94
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:40,131
I think this bastard is crazy.

95
00:05:40,923 --> 00:05:42,383
What is all this?

96
00:05:42,383 --> 00:05:45,595
He's been chugging alcohol from morning until now.

97
00:05:46,471 --> 00:05:50,058
Hey, Lee Seongjae.

98
00:05:50,058 --> 00:05:51,559
How much did you drink?

99
00:05:51,768 --> 00:05:52,935
Three bottles by yourself?

100
00:05:52,935 --> 00:05:53,603
Four bottles?

101
00:05:54,687 --> 00:05:57,774
Well, I think he drank a bit more than that.

102
00:06:06,616 --> 00:06:07,742
Hey.

103
00:06:07,867 --> 00:06:09,827
You'll die if you drink that.

104
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:20,046
How can I be in my right mind seeing him like this?

105
00:06:20,380 --> 00:06:21,756
Hey, even so.

106
00:06:21,756 --> 00:06:23,966
If Lee Seongjae finds out...

107
00:06:32,308 --> 00:06:33,393
Are you crazy?

108
00:06:34,018 --> 00:06:35,269
Let go.

109
00:06:35,770 --> 00:06:38,189
First, both of you calm down.

110
00:06:40,483 --> 00:06:41,567
Cha Dojin.

111
00:06:41,734 --> 00:06:42,443
Huh?

112
00:06:43,820 --> 00:06:45,822
Go home first.

113
00:06:51,327 --> 00:06:54,372
I'm leaving first.

114
00:07:08,177 --> 00:07:09,804
Do you really want to die?

115
00:07:09,846 --> 00:07:11,806
I won't die from drinking this.

116
00:07:13,307 --> 00:07:15,685
I said stop it.

117
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:25,027
I'm totally sobering up.

118
00:07:25,445 --> 00:07:27,697
Why are you acting like this?

119
00:07:27,947 --> 00:07:29,866
Shouldn't I be the one having a hard time?

120
00:07:30,324 --> 00:07:32,535
You're drunk.

121
00:07:32,535 --> 00:07:34,370
Let's talk again when you sober up.

122
00:07:34,912 --> 00:07:37,206
You get drunk and say all sorts of things,

123
00:07:37,206 --> 00:07:38,499
but I'm not allowed to?

124
00:07:39,375 --> 00:07:41,752
That's not what I mean.

125
00:07:51,721 --> 00:07:56,225
Every time you pushed me away,

126
00:07:56,225 --> 00:07:58,644
do you know how miserable I become?

127
00:08:00,354 --> 00:08:03,858
Convinced that you wouldn't know,

128
00:08:03,858 --> 00:08:07,361
I just hoped I could stay by your side.

129
00:08:07,653 --> 00:08:09,655
Why do you keep pushing me away?

130
00:08:10,031 --> 00:08:11,824
You were the one who couldn't be reached first.

131
00:08:12,992 --> 00:08:14,577
That's because...

132
00:08:15,244 --> 00:08:15,745
That's because...

133
00:08:15,745 --> 00:08:17,163
you found out.

134
00:08:20,875 --> 00:08:24,962
Now, all the things you do without any meaning,

135
00:08:24,962 --> 00:08:26,380
I can't accept them anymore.

136
00:08:29,383 --> 00:08:33,513
I wish I could've just drank and gotten drunk too.

137
00:08:34,347 --> 00:08:37,183
The things you do,

138
00:08:37,183 --> 00:08:40,811
the things you say,

139
00:08:40,811 --> 00:08:42,772
it would've been nice to forget them all.

140
00:08:45,358 --> 00:08:48,152
Sober, capturing every single expression of yours,

141
00:08:48,152 --> 00:08:51,280
engraving every single word you say... how do you think I feel?

142
00:08:52,573 --> 00:08:54,659
Kim Siwoo.

143
00:08:57,036 --> 00:08:59,038
I can't hold it in anymore.

144
00:09:00,581 --> 00:09:02,792
It's too hard to pretend that I'm fine.

145
00:09:04,502 --> 00:09:07,088
Every time you push me away,

146
00:09:08,464 --> 00:09:12,009
right here...

147
00:09:12,009 --> 00:09:15,304
right here hurts so much.

148
00:09:27,358 --> 00:09:28,985
I like you, Lee Seongjae.

149
00:09:31,571 --> 00:09:35,616
This is what I've wanted to say all along.

150
00:09:36,867 --> 00:09:40,705
Now I can never remain just a friend again.

151
00:10:11,861 --> 00:10:18,951
Now I can't pretend not to know anymore.
